Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time between 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for re-submissions
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time spent on 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' activities across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average time to reach 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' from the start of the process
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' for cases that are re-submitted and approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' back to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' across all re-submissions
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average waiting time before 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' is resolved or re-submitted
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR' for cases that are re-submitted and finally approved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time for all 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' activities to be corrected and re-submitted
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' before any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case

Name: Average time it takes for a declaration to be 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' after 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Average time for a declaration to go from 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' to being 'Payment Handled' for cases that are corrected and proceed to payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Total time for all cases where 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE' led to a final approval without further rejections
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE and the end of the case
